leadingComments.value:
*
 * Converts a string to a Title Case
 *
 * @category StringUtil
 * @param {String} string string to convert to Title Case
 * @returns {String} Returns a Tile Case string.
 * @example
 *
 * StringUtil.toTitleCase('the quick brown fox');
 * // => 'The Quick Brown Fox'
